*---------- Undocumented User Profile Primary Commands ----------*

Command   Description

NOINT     Generate PASSWORD NOINTERVAL commands for tablea entries
CKPW      Generate password change date for tablea entries
ALTUSER   Alter user selected segments
UNDOC     What you are reading now

*---------- Undocumented User Profile Line Commands -------------*

Command   Description

XR        Run IRRUT100 Cross Reference Report in Foreground
Z         Exclude a User profile from the list
